text: FIFA Football 2005 is a 2004 association football simulation video game in Electronic Arts' FIFA series created by EA Canada and published by Electronic Arts. It was released for the Playstation, Playstation 2, Playstation Portable, Xbox, GameCube, Game Boy Advance, N-Gage and Microsoft Windows.
